desc: Cafe, Breakfast & Ramen Bar. Single origin loose leaf tea, Ceremonial Matcha and small-batch roasted coffee. Creative soft serve ice cream bar. Vegan breakfast bowl, breakfast muffins and full breakfast box. Ramen, Katsu curry, rice bowl, poke, lo mein, grain salad pair with smoothie, bubble tea, cocktail and beer.

layout.text: The tea love affair is more than drinking tea
